(Overview) Tj
T*
(Functions show how each input is linked to exactly one output.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Learning Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Explain the meaning of Functions in Mathematics using accurate subject vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind input-output relationships, notation, and evaluation.) Tj
T*
(- Apply Functions to examples such as finding the value of f\(x\) for a given input.) Tj
T*
