(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Functions.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind input-output relationships,) Tj
T*
(notation, and evaluation.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct solution method step by step instead of jumping to the answer.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the result carefully and confirm that it matches the requirement of the topic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
