T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on finding the value of f\(x\) for a given input.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in input-output relationships, notation, and evaluation that) Tj
T*
(the question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Functions step by step without skipping reasoning.) Tj
